{"tid":1491862,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"好女友育成計劃（請絲不要進來）","createTime":"2019-08-20T14:56:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-21T05:54:33.000Z","uid":2419,"like":6,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d25bc08c883def09c868d8c49f26047da38bf804","tid":1491862,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T14:56:40.000Z","msg":"女朋友育成計劃🐰🧝🏻&zwj;♀️（不平等條約...誤）<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\nPart A Magic 🧟&zwj;♂️🧛🏻&zwj;♂️🧛🏽&zwj;♀️🧙🏻&zwj;♂️🧙🏿&zwj;♀️ Policy: <br />\n<br />\n- 起始底分為75 credits💘<br />\n- 每次換領獎勵均須以以下指引扣分🚥<br />\n- 每月只限換領不多於2次普通獎勵🌸<br />\n<br />\n*任何具爭議性項目之最終決定權均待🐸決定<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\nPart B 信用度評分表🍼🍬🍭<br />\n<br />\n100分（可換取🐷仔印x1，分數重置70分）<br />\n<br />\n90-99分 （好女友指數什佳🙉🐰可依分數換領獎賞🏅每次換領均扣取20分作服務費🎃）<br />\n<br />\n80-89分 （請完成以下加分任務🤹🏻&zwj;♀️以提升信用度）<br />\n<br />\n70-79分 （⛑瀕臨危險線🖤敬請自重）<br />\n<br />\n60-69分 （觸發懲罰機制，義務喂飽一餐膳食🍖）<br />\n<br />\n51-59分 （野外動向war game hunter🐧🐥🏹x1, 分數重置70分)<br />\n<br />\n50分以下 （🏥黑面無下限，吾覆任何wts 1天，1天後重置回70分）<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\nPart C 🛸可加可減機制🚀<br />\n<br />\n-5分系列<br />\n1. 遲到15分鐘以內<br />\n2. 迷戀/偷飲珍奶、喜茶等飲品🥤🥛🍯<br />\n<br />\n-10分系列<br />\n1. 遲到15-30分鐘<br />\n2. 消費過度，沒有節制，只因想要，而並非需要該物品👙👘👠👗👑<br />\n<br />\n-20分系列<br />\n1. 遲到30分鐘以上<br />\n3. 無故發牌氣🤬<br />\n4. 經常壟斷拍拖點、食飯點<br />\n5. 忘記約定/毀約🤯<br />\n<br />\n+5分系列<br />\n1. 制服play🍦<br />\n2. <br />\n3. 每月儲蓄3000$💰或以上<br />\n<br />\n+10分系列<br />\n1. 每月儲蓄4000-6000$💰<br />\n<br />\n+20分系列<br />\n1. <br />\n2. 做便當🍱<br />\n3. <br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\nPart D outstanding scholars🎖<br />\n<br />\n普通獎勵<br />\n1. 食好西一餐🥂🍷<br />\n2. 去靚靚打卡位影相一天遊📸<br />\n3. Extra dating day x1<br />\n4. 精緻小禮物🎁 (randomly choose)<br />\n5. 手作情信仔🦄💌<br />\n<br />\n隱藏大獎<br />\n1. 集齊20個肥🐷印可換取神秘大獎<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">基於小弟女友經常失控，本人決志設立育成計劃，供一眾巴參考參考，如有錯漏煩請多加提點，以作改善<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"a94501f3b5d1609d5c2a09de13e1b85641f124af","tid":1491862,"uid":238801,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T14:57:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">垃圾post 大家無視</span>"},{"pid":"4b4ffb431951f35809c1bbd8ae72f736694f4502","tid":1491862,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a94501f3b5d1609d5c2a09de13e1b85641f124af","tid":1491862,"uid":238801,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T14:57:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">垃圾post 大家無視</span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T14:57:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb0d82e54bafa8d811fecd14a01016cae3942e2c","tid":1491862,"uid":218575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a94501f3b5d1609d5c2a09de13e1b85641f124af","tid":1491862,"uid":238801,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T14:57:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">垃圾post 大家無視</span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T14:57:49.000Z","msg":"一早block咗"},{"pid":"23e0b43ef1d8adf1abed0821167ec15640d44f9f","tid":1491862,"uid":196556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T14:58:05.000Z","msg":"屌10次樓主老母"},{"pid":"1b6d51b5361a4df04f13d2695a143e752e6d67a4","tid":1491862,"uid":238801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b4ffb431951f35809c1bbd8ae72f736694f4502","tid":1491862,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a94501f3b5d1609d5c2a09de13e1b85641f124af","tid":1491862,"uid":238801,"like":5,"dislike":0,"s